      "label": "p_efficiency",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.2
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "p_efficiency",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "Perovskite solar cell efficiency can be continuously improved through materials engineering, interface engineering, and compositional engineering",
